description: Spells countered by Counterspell or Counterspell Ally will immediately burn a percentage of its mana cost from the enemy and deal damage based on the burned mana cost.
Anti-Mage gains damage when his enemies are at low mana.
Axe gains Strength based on his armor as long as he's away from his allies.
Berserker's Call gives attacking enemies more attack speed and Axe more armor for the duration.
Bane has increased attack speed when attacking Nightmared units.
Nightmared units walk in Bane's chosen direction.
Ruptured units are pushed when attacked by Bloodseeker.
Bloodrage silences the target and can be applied to enemies. Bloodrage increases base attack damage instead of spell damage.
Crystal Nova has increased radius and grants allied heroes a physical damage barrier. Barrier is increased for Crystal Maiden.
Activating Arcane Aura temporarily increases Crystal Maiden's spell amplification and mana costs. During the duration, Crystal Maiden restores her and her allies' Mana when casting spells.
Drow deals 30% more damage when attacking from high ground.
Drow can move slowly and use items while casting Multishot.
Aftershock radius is increased by 40 for every level of Echo Slam.
Enemy heroes stunned by Fissure emit an echo to each nearby unit.
Blade Fury can now critically strike based on the level of Blade Dance.
Juggernaut gains Agility and Movement Speed as long as he's not taking damage.
Starstorm's second meteor deals more damage and blinds the target.
Upon landing, Leap roots targets in a 250 radius for 1.5 =1.75 =2.0 =2.25s.
Morphling's Primary Attribute is now Agility. Waveform attacks enemies in his path.
Morphling's Primary Attribute is now Strength. Adaptive Strike stuns based on Morphling's strength. Morphling gains 1% Spell Amp per 4 Agility.
Presence of the Dark Lord temporarily reduces more armor after nearby enemy heroes are killed. Every hero kill increases Necromastery's max souls by 1 until Shadow Fiend dies.
Shadowraze slows enemies.
Juxtapose Illusions spawn on random nearby units and deal more damage but can't be controlled.
Spirit Lances from Phantom Lancer's illusions deal 25% Lance Damage.
Waning Rift can push or pull targets.
Puck's Illusory Orb can be curved in any direction, moves faster, deals more damage and lasts longer.
Dismember increases Strength when dealing damage to heroes.
While Rot is activated, Pudge gains bonus attack damage every second.
Storm Surge lightning strikes more often and hits all units within Eye of the Storm's area of effect when it is active.
Razor gains 1.25% spell amplification for every 20 points of attack damage.
When Sand King attacks enemies in Sand Storm, he applies a blinding debuff to his target.
A Caustic Finale explosion is created around every enemy hero hit in Stinger's innermost radius.
Electric Vortex applies a debuff that triggers an Overload Charge if they attack.
Static Remnants spawn at Storm Spirit and move to the target position.
Warcry provides a physical damage barrier.
Sven gains additional attack damage from Strength.
Tossed units slow and deal bonus damage to other targets at the Toss destination.
Tiny gains Status and Slow Resistance from Strength. Slow Resistance also reduces the impact of Attack Speed slows.
Magic Missile deals 0.75 bonus damage for every creep the enemy has killed.
Vengeful Spirit's ranged attacks behave as if they were melee attacks.
Shackleshot affects more enemies and grants damage per unit shackled.
Powershot executes low health enemy heroes.
Static Field deals more damage to nearby enemies.
When Thundergod's Wrath kills an enemy, it deals more damage to the other enemies.
Tidebringer cooldown is reduced per enemy hero it hits.
When X Marks the Spot returns its target, Kunkka and all nearby allies gain Ghostship's Admiral's Rum buff.
Casting Laguna Blade temporarily supercharges Lina, granting her stacks of Fiery Soul.
Lina's spells deal extra damage over time.
Mana Drain deals damage equal to 100% of mana stolen.
Lion gains a strong Melee cleaving attack after casting Finger of Death.
Shadow Shaman's attacks can transform enemies into a chicken.
Summons a single massive Serpent Ward with 12x damage and 10x health and bounty values.
Slardar has slow resistance and even more movement speed at the beginning of Guardian Sprint.
Corrosive Haze increases Slardar's armor by 50% of the total armor reduced.
Kraken Shell gains permanent Damage Block when an enemy hero dies under the effects of Anchor Smash.
Tidehunter grows larger and gains extra bonuses per level.
Death Ward attacks multiple targets with reduced damage.
Enemies dying while Maledicted explode.
When an enemy is killed by Chain Frost or while under the effect of Frost Shield, the duration of these abilities is extended.
Sinister Gaze applies a lingering effect to the target, causing it to take extra magic damage from Lich and amplify incoming movement slows.
Riki receives bonus experience for assists and kills.
Tricks of the Trade has 4.5x Agility Bonus when attacking non-hero units. When Riki kills a non-hero unit during Tricks of the Trade, the cooldown is reduced by 0.75s.
Units in a 600 radius moving away from Enigma have a 8% movespeed penalty.
Enigma spawns Eidolons upon receiving damage.
March of the Machines applies a non-stacking heal over time when passing through allied heroes.

When a Self-Defense Matrix barrier on Tinker is fully absorbed, he blinks in a random forward direction.

DISPEL TYPE: Basic Dispel
While Take Aim is active, Sniper's attacks do not reveal him from fog of war.
Shrapnel slow and damage are increased, but duration is decreased.
Sadist also grants Necrophos' AoE abilities and items bonus Radius per kill.
Ghost Shroud steals speed from his enemies and decreases their restorative powers.
Chaotic Offering Golems deal more burn damage based on Warlock's health and mana regeneration.
Grants Warlock the item Black Grimoire, which can be consumed to gain experience for each kill Warlock participated in. Starts with 1 charge.
Beastmaster attacks faster when his units are nearby.
Beastmaster can get a self attack speed and damage amplification boost.
Queen of Pain has bonus Spell Amplification but a percentage of her spell damage is reflected back to her.
Queen of Pain returns spell damage back to enemies. Succubus's Spell Lifesteal also applies to Pure & Magical reflected damage.
Noxious Plague spreads again.
When Venomous Gale impacts enemy heroes, 2 Plague Wards are created around them. Plague Wards also deal Septic Shock damage based on their attack damage.
Faceless Void can cast Chronosphere, trapping enemies in a sphere.
Faceless Void can cast Time Zone, dramatically slowing down enemies and speeding up allies in an area.
Wraith King can summon skeletons to fight for him.
Wraith King's attacks curse enemies, dealing additional damage after a delay.
Hero deaths empower your next Exorcism.
Death Prophet delays a percentage of incoming damage, taking the damage in even intervals over a short duration.
Coup de Grace procs every 6 attacks on the same hero or 4 attacks on non hero units.
Stifling Dagger re-casts when an enemy dies.
Nether Ward restores mana and health to Pugna based on how much damage is dealt.
Pugna receives 1.5% spell amplification per destroyed tower.
Meld bonus damage and armor reductions are applied to all enemies in the Psi Blades split range.
Refraction gains a damage charge every time a shield charge gets consumed.
After Poison Attack stacks expire, enemies around the target take additional damage.
Viper's Corrosive Skin effects are increased while he is in Nethertoxin.
Lunar Orbit provide damage reduction while active.
Hitting enemies with Lucent Beams or Eclipse grants Luna bonus attack damage.
Dragon Knight deals additional Magic Damage with his attacks. Dragon Knight's abilities have increased Area of Effect that get stronger when in Elder Dragon Form.
Dragon Knight has Corrosive Powers on his attacks that get stronger when in Elder Dragon Form. All of his abilities deal Physical damage.
Dragon Knight has Slow and Health Restoration Reduction Effects on his attacks that get stronger when in Elder Dragon Form.
Dazzle's overhealing is converted into a barrier. Weave is stronger on allies and amplifies incoming heals from Dazzle.
Dazzle can spread his Poison Touch when attacking enemies. Weave is stronger on enemies.
Power Cogs form in a larger radius.
Leshrac's attacks restore mana.
Diabolic Edict explosion rate increased but it no longer damages buildings.
After Sprout is cast, all trees in a 1200 radius heal nearby allies.
Whenever Nature's Prophet kills an enemy hero or one dies nearby, a money tree is created in their place that drops gold bags to be collected.
Feast's max HP per hero kill is increased. Open Wounds' cooldown is refreshed if a unit dies while afflicted by Open Wounds.
Consuming a creep with Infest drenches enemies in blood which deals damage over time based on the host's remaining health. Infest can be used on Ancient creeps.
Dark Seer also gains Attack Speed from Intelligence.
Dark Seer moves faster when near other heroes.
Strafe attacks cause enemies to miss more often.
Death Pact teleports Clinkz towards his victim. Reduces Death Pact cooldown.
Omniknight deals more damage to heroes inside his Degen Aura.
Ability damage done to enemies by Omniknight heals him over time.
Summon Healing Wisps upon receiving damage.
Enchant and attacks on Enchanted targets have extra range.
Berserker's Blood can be activated for a health cost. Dispels Huskar, then after a delay, heals for the amount of health consumed plus an additional bonus per debuff dispelled.
Burning Spears also burns enemies for a percentage of their max health. Costs Max Health instead of Current Health.
The game now starts at night instead of day. Night is longer than day. Night Stalker starts with a bonus level of Hunter in the Night.
Increases the max level of Void. Level 5 Void at night becomes ground targeted and applies to an area.
Reduces health regeneration of enemies on webs.
Insatiable Hunger also applies to nearby Spiderlings.
Shuriken Toss applies its damage and slow to all enemies it passes through.
Bounty Hunter steals gold when targeting enemy heroes with his abilities or items.
Shukuchi movespeed increased and slows enemies when passing through them.
Weaver gains experience when The Swarm beetles attack heroes.
Jakiro deals more damage with his double attacks.
Ice Path lasts longer and detonates upon expiration, dealing damage and stunning enemies a second time. Ice Path can be manually detonated early.
Firefly also lights Batrider on fire. He gains increasingly more Move Speed and Spell Amplification and burns away a portion of his max health each second.
Increases the max level of Sticky Napalm. Level 5 Sticky Napalm causes every attack to apply 1 stack of Sticky Napalm.
Summon Convert calls forth either a Hellbear or Hellbear Smasher.
Summon Convert calls forth either a Satyr Mindstealer or Satyr Tormenter.
Reality also casts Spectral Dagger on the target.
Ancient Apparition's abilities reduce the enemy's Strength.
Cold Feet applies in an AoE, depending on the current level of Ice Blast.
Devour now has 2 charges and stolen creep abilities are upgraded by one level.
Doom can sell items for 85% of their value, but his buyback costs are increased by 20%.
Every 6.66 minutes, Doom's duration is increased by 0.66s.
When damaged during Enrage, Ursa gains bonus attack damage.
Debuffs inflicted by Ursa last longer.
Charge of Darkness bonus movement speed lingers after charge ends.
Greater Bash chance is increased if you've bashed more than one hero recently.
Call Down creates delayed secondary explosions around heroes it hits.
Every successful hit of a Rocket Barrage rocket on an enemy hero increases Gyrocopter's movement speed.
Alchemist starts with 250 more gold.
Unstable Concoction and Berserk Potion recharge faster when in Chemical Rage.
Alchemist gains +70 GPM for each Aghanim's Scepter he has granted to allies.

Quas gains an additional max level. When Invoker reaches level 6, Quas gains an additional level.

Aghanim's Scepter upgrades Ice Wall.

Aghanim's Shard upgrades Ghost Walk.

Wex gains an additional max level. When Invoker reaches level 6, Wex gains an additional level.

Aghanim's Scepter upgrades Tornado.

Aghanim's Shard upgrades E.M.P.

Exort gains an additional max level. When Invoker reaches level 6, Exort gains an additional level.

Aghanim's Scepter upgrades Sun Strike.

Aghanim's Shard upgrades Sun Strike.
Increases the max level of Glaives of Wisdom. Level 5 Glaives of Wisdom bounce 1 time to a random target within 450 range.
Silencer takes less damage from and deals more damage to silenced targets.
When Essence Flux restores mana, it also temporarily increases maximum mana.
Heroes affected by Astral Imprisonment and Sanity's Eclipse heal Outworld Destroyer every time they cast a spell.
Enemy heroes killed by Lycan or his units extend Shapeshift duration.
Increases the max level of Summon Wolves while lowering the max level of Howl and Feral Impulse.
Throw a barrel at enemies, damaging them and applying Cinder Brew.
When brewed up, Brewmaster moves with a varying amount of movement speed, altering between 15% slower and 50% faster for the duration.
Disseminate instantly removes a percentage of the opponent's health for its duration.
Shadow Demon creates illusions of heroes that die near him.
Spirit Link's Shared Armor is increased and Lone Druid's attacks heal the Spirit Bear.
Reality Rift has equal chances of applying Break, Disarm, or Silence for 50% of the base debuff duration in addition to its normal effects.
Chaos Knight can craft artifacts from the next tier when making a Neutral Item.
Chaos Bolt splits in half upon striking its target, stunning one additional enemy and damaging another.
Obtain extra Meepos sooner and get 1 extra Meepo.
Meepos increase other Meepos' attack speed and armor.
Treant gains +{s:attack_damage_per_level} base attack damage per hero level.
Leech Seed can be ground targeted to plant a tree.
Multicast chance is increased by  0.06% of Ogre Magi's Strength.
Level requirement of all spells and talents reduced by 1. You get 0 Ability Points at level one and 3 Ability Points at level two.
While transformed into a Flesh Golem, attacks spawn a zombie.
Casting Soul Rip on allies increases their Strength by a percentage of Undying's Strength.
Stolen spells also have lower mana cost.
Casting a spell temporarily increases the area of effect for all subsequent spells.
Thunder Strike additionally hits all enemies within Kinetic Field. Thunder Strike Slow duration is doubled.
Replaces Kinetic Field with the ability to create impassable walls.
Electromagnetic Repulsion can be activated manually, be cast on allies and deals damage equal to a percentage of Disruptor's current health.
Mind Flare burns a percentage of the target's max mana.
For the first 15s of Vendetta, Nyx Assassin is hasted and has unobstructed pathing.
Every 6 attacks from Naga and her illusions, enemies around them are damaged and their Armor is reduced.
Naga Siren can create a splash around herself and her illusions, damaging enemies and capping their max movement speed.
Grants the Solar Bind ability while active.

After a short delay, teleports the targeted friendly hero to your location. If the targeted friendly hero takes player based damage during this time, the ability is interrupted. When cast, the teleport target's movement speed is increased. Upon teleporting, the increased movement speed buff are applied to both Keeper of the Light and the teleport target, and the latter also receives a Chakra Magic.

 If alt-cast, teleports Keeper of the Light to the target Ally instead. 

 Ability Level increases with levels of Spirit Form.
Overcharge grants attack speed and spell amplification to Io and any Tethered allies.
Overcharge grants armor and magic resistance to Io and any Tethered allies.
Grave Chill also affects units around the target. Visage can also recall his familiars.
Soul Assumption kills give bonus gold. Visage can also recall his familiars.
Pounce applies stacks of Essence Shift when striking enemy heroes.
Barracuda lingers after being revealed to the enemy if Slark is not nearby allied heroes. Slark's attacks reduce the target's armor while Slark is under the effects of Barracuda.
Every 6 attacks, Medusa applies poison to her arrow that briefly reduces movement speed and attack speed.
Medusa's movement speed is fixed at 310 (465 during Stone Gaze). Medusa is unslowable and does not benefit from movement speed increases.
Fervor grants armor per stack while in melee form.
During Battle Trance, Troll Warlord has increased max Fervor stacks and no attack speed limit. Battle Trance grants allied heroes 50% of the attack speed bonus.
Double Edge damage is increased when Centaur is damage by enemies.
Centaur Warrunner gains Movement Speed based on his Strength.
Empower is always on Magnus. Each subsequent attack increases its power.
Increases the max level of Shockwave. Level 5 Shockwave causes it to return towards Magnus's location.
Timber Chain splinters the tree into all directions around Timbersaw.

Launches a second independent Chakram that follows a curved path and returns to Timbersaw, damaging and slowing enemies it passes through. Enemies caught in the saw blade will move more slowly for every 5% of health missing.
Bristleback now fires Viscous Nasal Goo instead of Quills when damaged. Viscous Nasal Goo effects are stronger.
Warpath can be activated to gain extra bonuses. While Seeing Red, Bristleback's vision is limited and he does not receive vision from his allies.
Tusk can cast Tag Team causing nearby enemies to receive bonus damage from attacks.
Tusk can cast Drinking Buddies, pulling him and a teammate closer and granting both bonus Movement Speed and Attack Damage.
Skywrath Mage gains a magic damage barrier when dealing damage to heroes.
Skywrath Mage's Cooldowns are reduced when he deals spell damage to enemy heroes.
Units dying nearby Abaddon lower his cooldowns.
Mist Coil also deals 40 =60 =80 =100% attack damage and applies effects from items and abilities. Self Damage increased when targeting enemies.
Natural Order drains Magic Resistance and Armor over time.
Elder Titan's Base Attack Speed is reduced but his Movement Speed also grants Attack Speed.
Overwhelming Odds grants an all damage barrier based on the damage it deals to enemy heroes.

When a Duel is won, units that damaged the loser during the Duel will gain permanent bonus damage. If Legion Commander won the Duel, she will automatically cast Press the Attack on herself and assisting allies.
Techies gains 1 attack range and attack projectile speed for each point of attack speed.
Increased Blast Off! damage and self damage.
Techies stack all previously selected Enchantments onto newly crafted Neutral Items.
Sleight of Fist hits one of its targets an extra time.
Searing Chains can affect two additional enemies. When Searing Chains are cast, they are also cast around each Fire Remnant.
Gain bonus Attack Damage when Magnetizing Stone Remnants.
Stone Remnant has a {s:bonus_AbilityCooldown}s cooldown instead of Charges and Remnants don't get destroyed by Rolling Boulder.
Rolling Boulder can roll over allied heroes for additional bonuses.
Underlord's attacks cleave while he has bonus damage from Atrophy Aura.
Fiend's Gate periodically summons minions.
There is no minimum health threshold for Sundered enemies.
Conjure Image illusions always spawn at full health and cost health instead of mana.
Phoenix deals 4.5% of his missing health as magic damage to all enemies in a 400 radius every second.
Sun Ray deals more damage and applies more Blinding Sun stacks towards the tip of the ray.
Spell amplification increased by 1% per hero level.
Heal amplification increased by 0.75% per hero level.
Cold Embrace can be cast on buildings. Does not heal buildings. Allied units and buildings gain bonus attack damage when emerging from the icy cocoon.
Winter's Curse is recast on the lowest health enemy hero if the primary target dies.

The Tempest Double is infused with the bonuses of Power Runes for 12s when created.

Level 1 - Arcane Rune.

Level 2 - Arcane and Invisibility Runes.

Level 3 - Arcane, Invisibility, and Haste Runes.
Magnetic Field pulls runes. Arc Warden gains +1.5 all attributes permanently upon activating a Power Rune.
Increases the max level of Tree Dance. Level 5 Tree Dance reduces the cooldown to zero.
Monkey King can transform into one of his soldiers during Wukong's command.
Dark Willow deals more damage to nearby heroes when she's in the Shadow Realm.

Cursed Crown accumulates all damage dealt by Dark Willow and attack damage dealt by her allies. A percentage of that damage is dealt again as magical damage to the whole area when the counter expires.
Pangolier can double jump with Shield Crash dealing more damage and gaining more barrier.
Rolling Thunder movement and turn speed increased, but duration is decreased.
Ink Swell can be manually detonated early.
Stroke of Fate additionally launches a reflected curved stroke from the right hand.
Scurry also provides bonus attack and cast range.
Sharpshooter has a greatly reduced cooldown. Damage, debuff duration, turn time, and wind-up times are also reduced.
Resonant Pulse creates a larger all damage barrier instead of a physical barrier.
Upon exiting Dissimilate, Aether Remnants are created at the 3 portals furthest from Void Spirit.
Whenever Snapfire glances or misses an attack, 2 ricochet attacks will bounce towards nearby enemies.
Scatterblast is narrower and longer. Bonus damage and slow when enemies are not in point blank range.
Mars and his allies gain health, mana, and attack damage when an enemy inside his Arena of Blood dies.
Enemies inside the Arena of Blood don't have vision outside the arena.
Ringmaster's Souvenirs are Funhouse Mirror, Strongman Tonic, and Whoopee Cushion.
Ringmaster's Souvenirs are Crystal Ball, Unicycle, and Weighted Pie.
Whenever Dawnbreaker hits a target with a powered up Luminosity, she decreases the cooldowns of all of her abilities.
Dawnbreaker and nearby allies gain bonus attack speed at the end of Starbreaker for each swipe that hit enemy heroes.
Walking along Celestial Hammer's fire trail gives bonus movespeed.
Rebound can be alt-cast to bring Marci's ally with her after the jump.
Upon landing with Rebound, Marci gains a Fury combo.
Gain 3 Uproar stacks upon being disabled by an enemy hero.
Each Pulverize slam increase Primal Beast's AoE.
The Calling becomes stronger when heroes die inside it.

Dead Shot fears increase Gunslinger chance.

Gunslinger procs reduce Dead Shot cooldown.
Kez deals extra damage on the first attack or ability after switching to Katana, and gains bonus movement speed after switching to Sai.
Triggering a Shodo Sai Mark from invisibility deals bonus critical damage. Increases Raven's Veil invisibility duration.
